## ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA

- [ ] Max 5 primary sections (+ optional news teaser)
- [ ] Primary CTA visible above fold and in final CTA band
- [ ] All content from canon or labeled placeholders
- [ ] Light mode, Sakura pink accents, generous whitespace
- [ ] LCP-friendly hero (optimized images, no giant video)
- [ ] WCAG AA contrast on all text/background pairs

